# Decision Table Testing

Decision Table Testing is used when system behavior depends on multiple conditions.

## Example
Login functionality

### Conditions
- Correct username
- Correct password

### Actions
- Allow login
- Show error message

## Decision Table

| Username Correct | Password Correct | Result           |
|------------------|------------------|------------------|
| Yes              | Yes              | Login successful |
| Yes              | No               | Error message    |
| No               | Yes              | Error message    |
| No               | No               | Error message    |

## Conclusion
Decision tables help ensure all combinations of conditions are tested.
